<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.9.5">
<l>vāṅkunīr malarulaki ṉiṟpaṉavun tirivaṉavu</l>
<l>māṅkuyirkaḷ piṟappiṟappup piṇimūppā ṟakarppuṇṇu</l>
<l>mīṅkitaṉmēl vennaraka mivaiyeṉṉa vulakiyaṟkai</l>
<l>vāṅkeṉainī maṇivaṇṇā vaṭiyēṉai maṟukkēlē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who stand and those who move around in the flower world [girded] by the dragging water,</l>
<l>the living beings there undergo being broken to pieces by birth, death, sickness [and] old age.</l>
<l>Here after this [comes] hot hell. What are these? The nature of the world.</l>
<l>Drag me, you with sapphire colour, do not refuse me, [your] servant.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
